# 🏦 SAB Digital Banking System

A fully functional digital banking system built with Python and SQLite. This project demonstrates the intersection of **financial accounting principles** and **software development**.

## 🎥 Demo

[Watch the Demo](https://youtu.be/TNU2_saHBkA)

*Click the link above to watch a 3-minute walkthrough*

## Features

### Security & Authentication
- User login with 4-digit PIN validation
- Secure access to individual accounts
- Input sanitization and error handling

### Account Management
- Available Balance (spending account)
- Savings Account
- Expenses Tracking
- Car Insurance
- Income Account
- Medical Bills

### Transaction Processing
- Deposit to Income account
- Transfer from Income to Available Balance
- Payments to Savings, Expenses, Insurance, Medical Bills
- Beneficiary payments (Ivy, Brand, Dave, Quinton)
- Real-time balance updates

### Audit & Reporting
- Complete transaction history
- Mini statement generation
- Timestamp logging for all transactions
- Balance verification after each transaction

### Data Persistence
- SQLite database integration
- Multi-user support
- Data survives program restarts
- Transaction logs never lost

